snippet.textDisplay: It was a long time wish to see both Shafqat Amanat and Ahmed Jehanzeb (one with sparkly jacket) together and behold here it is. Thank you coke studio, what a brilliant start to season 10. I would love to see some more on classical theme, perhaps Shafqat and Rahat together.. listening to this hamd with subtitles is even more fascinating though I'm native urdu speaker. I just want to share this song to the rest of the world especially on western media social platforms.. how beautiful and peaceful is the Zikr of Allah SWT. Loved the bit from 5.40 on wards especially when Shafqat says MERE IRADEY JO TOOTEY TO MUJH KO PATA YE CHALA (when all my grand schemes fell apart, I came to know...) I guess a lot of us really recognize Allah SWT when this happens to us and we really then realize that we are not in control of our lives.. we never were and we'll never be.. and the feeling of Nidamat that what we have been thinking through all our life and making plans and deciding what's best for us and what we should do.. it was not us.. never us... this is the real meaning of Tauheed. May Allah SWT help us all in keeping on a straight path and following nothing but His commands. Ameen.
